subject: Head Office
body:
Head Office
935 Pennsylvania Avenue, NW
Washington, DC 20535 USA
Dear Beneficiary,
My name is Christopher A Wray, I'm the Director of the Federal Bureau
of Investigation, serving since 2017.
I have good news for you.
Reply back as soon as possible.
Yours sincerely,
Christopher Wray
christopherwray222023@outlook.com

subject: Re:   Head Office
body:
Hello there,

Thank you for reaching out to me. It's not every day that I receive a message from someone as important as the Director of the Federal Bureau! I'm quite intrigued by your message, especially when you mentioned about some good news. Could you please share more details about this good news? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
James
